      <description>Wayne Thevenot worked with Gillis Long during the 1980s and was his
            campaign manager at one time. Gillis Long (1923-1985) was representative for the 8th
            U.S. Congressional District of Louisiana in 1963-1965 and 1973-1985. He ran
            unsuccessfully for governor of Louisiana in 1964 and 1971.</description>
